==English==

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-percolate.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Verb===
{{en-verb|percolates|percolating|percolated}}

# To [[filter]] a [[liquid]] through a [[porous]] substance.
# To [[pass]] or [[ooze]] through something.
# To make ([[coffee]]) in a [[percolator]].
# {{intransitive}} To [[drain]] or [[seep]] through a porous substance.
# {{figurative}} To [[mull]] over an idea for a while, to let the thoughts seep through.

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[liquid]] that has been percolated.

